{
  "texts": [
    "We employed the \"one trial per run\" data collection method, as in Experiment 1.",
    "Comprehensive details of the experimental procedure can be accessed in the preregistration report available at https://osf.io/t5nes.",
    "In total, 2,368 experimental items were tested, with each item undergoing 50 experimental runs.",
    "Figure 4 illustrates a strong correlation between by-item rating scores of ChatGPT and humans (r = 0.72, p < 0.001).",
    "Figure 5 shows that when comparing average rating scores across participant types and grammaticality manipulations, grammatical sentences consistently received notably higher acceptability ratings than ungrammatical ones."
  ]
}